column2: SELECT  s.mjd, s.plate, s.fiberID, g.oiii_#_flux, g.oiii_#_eqw, g.h_beta_flux, g.h_beta_eqw, g.h_alpha_flux, g. h_alpha_eqw, g.nii_#_flux, g.nii_#_eqw, w.w1mpro as w1, w.w2mpro as w2, w.w3mpro as w3 FROM WISE_xmatch AS x JOIN WISE_allsky AS w ON x.wise_cntr = w.cntr JOIN (SELECT * FROM SpecPhotoAll  WHERE  SpecPhotoAll.nChild = #) AS p ON x.sdss_objid = p.objid JOIN (SELECT * FROM SpecObjAll  WHERE  SpecObjAll.z < # AND SpecObjAll.snmedian_g > # AND SpecObjAll.snmedian_r > #) AS s ON s.specobjid = p.specobjid JOIN (SELECT * FROM GalSpecLine  WHERE GalSpecLine.sigma_balmer < #/# AND GalSpecLine.oiii_#_flux > # AND GalSpecLine.h_beta_flux > # AND GalSpecLine.h_alpha_flux > # AND GalSpecLine.nii_#_flux > # AND GalSpecLine.oiii_#_flux > #*GalSpecLine.oiii_#_flux_err AND GalSpecLine.h_beta_flux > #*GalSpecLine.h_beta_flux_err AND GalSpecLine.h_alpha_flux > #*GalSpecLine.h_alpha_flux_err AND GalSpecLine.nii_#_flux > #*GalSpecLine.nii_#_flux_err) AS g ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid WHERE (s.class = &&& or s.class = &&&)
